# On Cloudflare the Worker serves BOTH the client and the API at the same
# origin, so leave this EMPTY — the client uses relative /api/* paths (and
# wss:// for live) which hit the Worker itself. Only set an absolute origin if
# the client is hosted on a DIFFERENT origin than the API (e.g. a standalone
# Node/Render backend).
VITE_API_URL=
